<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../494/9865494.xml">
Contract on Cherry Street</link></psychological_feature>
</show>
</movie>
</social_event>
</event>
</artifact>
</creation>
</product>
</it>.</p>
<p>

Balsam starred as Murray Klein on the <it><series wordnetid="108457976" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../246/163246.xml">
All in the Family</link></series>
</it> <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../212/63212.xml">
spin-off</link> <it><series wordnetid="108457976" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../749/803749.xml">
Archie Bunker's Place</link></series>
</it> for two seasons (1979-1981). In 1967, he won a <award wordnetid="106696483" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../741/54741.xml">
Tony Award</link></award>
 for his appearance in the 1967 <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../252/725252.xml">
Broadway</link> production of <it><link>
You Know I Can't Hear You When the Water's Running</link></it>.</p>

